#: en/handbook/hb-install-x86+amd64-bootloader.xml:397
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you are using a non-multilib <uri\n"
"link=\"?part=1&amp;chap=6#doc_chap2\">profile</uri> and still intend to use the\n"
